aus deputies out looking for suspects|last=Farrow|first=Deke|date=March 9, 2020|website=The Modesto Bee|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=March 11, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 8, 2020}}\n|[[Milwaukee|Milwaukee, Wisconsin]]\n|1\n|3\n|'''4'''\n|An early morning argument escalated and resulted in one man killed and three injured outside a local business.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fox6now.com/2020/03/08/quadruple-shooting-leaves-1-dead-near-35th-fairmount-suspect-in-custody/|title=\u2018A security guard got shot:\u2019 1 killed, 1 critical in quadruple shooting at Cheetah Club|date=2020-03-08|website=FOX6Now.com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 8, 2020}}\n|[[South Holland, Illinois]]\n|0\n|4\n|'''4'''\n|Four men were wounded in a vehicle on [[Interstate 94 in Illinois|Bishop Ford Freeway]], after another vehicle's occupant(s) fired on them.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://abc7chicago.com/5996668/|title=4 injured in Bishop Ford Freeway shooting in South Holland, ISP says|last=D'Onofrio|first=Jessica|date=2020-03-09|website=ABC7 Chicago|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 8, 2020}}\n|[[Rosedale, Maryland]]\n|1\n|5\n|'''6'''\n|A 13-year-old boy was killed, five others were wounded; a 14-year-old boy and girl, two 12-year-old boys and a 19-year-old man were wounded. The group was shot at in a parking lot after an altercation while attending a Triple Threat Elite Dance event.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://foxbaltimore.com/news/local/report-of-multiple-people-shot-1-killed-at-baltimore-county-shopping-center|title=13-yr-old killed, other juveniles and 19-yr-old injured in Baltimore County shooting|last=Kemp|first=Micarie|date=2020-03-08|website=WBFF|access-date=2020-03-09}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 7, 2020}}\n|[[Cleveland|Cleveland, Ohio]]\n|1\n|17\n|'''18'''\n|Seventeen people were wounded and one killed after a shootout between multiple motorcycle clubs after a fi