ation-store-charts-september-gta5-and-killzone-mercenary-take-top-honours/ |title=PlayStation Store charts, September: GTA5 and Killzone Mercenary take top honours |last=Dutton |first=Fred |work=[[PlayStation Blog]] |publisher=[[Sony Computer Entertainment]] |date=October 7, 2013 |accessdate=March 7, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6WqOMv1sK?url=http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2013/10/07/playstation-store-charts-september-gta5-and-killzone-mercenary-take-top-honours/ |archivedate=March 7, 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PSL 8 Million\">{{cite web|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/09/01/the-last-of-us-remastered-sales-crosses-1-million-sold-worldwide/ |title=The Last of Us Remastered Crosses One Million Sold Worldwide |last=Dunning |first=Jason |work=PlayStation LifeStyle |publisher=[[CraveOnline]] |date=September 1, 2014 |accessdate=February 13, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XBQcBxR5?url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/09/01/the-last-of-us-remastered-sales-crosses-1-million-sold-worldwide/ |archivedate=March 21, 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<!-- Awards -->\n\n<ref name=\"Decade Mashable\">{{cite web |url=https://mashable.com/article/15-favorites-video-games-2010s/ |title=Our 15 favorite video games from the 2010s |work=[[Mashable]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |date=October 15, 2019 |accessdate=December 9, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021043710/https://mashable.com/article/15-favorites-video-games-2010s/ |archivedate=October 21, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Decade MC\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-videogames-of-the-decade-2010s |title=The Best Video Games of the Decade (2010-19), According to Game Critics |work=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=December 9, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208051915/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-videogames-of-the-decade-2010s |archivedate=December 8, 2019 |