 day. He is currently under quarantine at a hospital in Tokyo.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3F6D1GN3FULBJ00N.html|title=\u30a4\u30bf\u30ea\u30a2\u304b\u3089\u306e\u5e30\u56fd\u8005\u3001\u521d\u306e\u30b3\u30ed\u30ca\u611f\u67d3\u78ba\u8a8d\u3000\u90fd\u5185\u3067\u5165\u9662 (\"Returnee from Italy tests positive for coronavirus; in hospital in Tokyo\")|language=Japanese|agency=Asahi Shimbun|date=2020-03-13|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Jordan]]''' \u2013\nOn 2 March, Jordan confirmed that a man in his 30s who had returned from Italy two weeks earlier had tested positive, with other potential cases under observation.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arab.news/v47zf|title=Jordan announces first coronavirus case from Italy|date=2 March 2020|website=Arab News|access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Zehra Nur D\u00fcz |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/en/health/jordan-confirms-first-coronavirus-case/1752064|title=Jordan confirms first coronavirus case|agency=Anadolu Agency|date=2020-03-02|access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Mainland China]]''' \u2013\nOn 1 March, [[Qingtian County]], [[Lishui]], [[Zhejiang]] confirmed its first imported case, a 31-year-old Chinese woman who had worked at a restaurant in [[Bergamo]].<ref>{{cite web |script-title=zh:\u4e3d\u6c34\u65b0\u589e1\u4f8b\u610f\u5927\u5229\u8f93\u5165\u6027\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b\uff1a31\u5c81\u9752\u7530\u5973\u5b50\u4ece\u610f\u5927\u5229\u5230\u8fbe\u4e0a\u6d77\u6d66\u4e1c\u673a\u573a |url=https://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/kejiao/content/2020-03/02/content_7686772.htm |language=zh-cn |website=hangzhou.com.cn |date=2020-03-02|access-date=2020-03-02}}</ref> On 2 March, seven more imported cases were confirmed in Qingtian County that are related to the first imported case.<ref>{{cite web |script-title=zh:\u6d59\u6c5f\u9752\u7530\u53bf\u65b0\u589e7\u4f8b\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u5165\u75c5\u4f8b \u66fe\u5728\u610f\u5927\u5229\u540c\u4e00\u9910\u5385\u5de5\u4f5c |url=http://www.bjd.com