ou]], [[Henan]] confirmed the first imported case, who stay in Italy.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.dahe.cn/2020/03-11/616366.html|title=\u9690\u7792\u5883\u5916\u884c\u7a0b\uff0c\u90d1\u5dde\u4e00\u7537\u5b50\u786e\u8bca\uff0c\u8b66\u65b9\u5df2\u7acb\u6848\u4fa6\u67e5|publisher=dahe.cn|date=2020-03-11|accessdate=2020-03-11}}</ref> On 12 March, Shanghai confirmed one more imported case.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://wsjkw.sh.gov.cn/xwfb/20200313/74e7fafee4ea4df4b676db66ee4098de.html|title=\u6628\u65e512-24\u65f6\uff0c\u4e0a\u6d77\u65b0\u589e2\u4f8b\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u5165\u578b\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u80ba\u708e\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b|date=2020-03-13|accessdate=2020-03-13|publisher=Shanghai Municipal Health Commission}}</ref> On 13 March, Shanghai confirmed four more imported cases.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://wsjkw.sh.gov.cn/xwfb/20200314/1bf09cb0fdd147ea878c8e95e849f41e.html|title=\u6628\u65e512-24\u65f6\uff0c\u4e0a\u6d77\u65b0\u589e4\u4f8b\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u5165\u578b\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u80ba\u708e\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b|date=2020-03-14|accessdate=2020-03-14|publisher=Shanghai Municipal Health Commission}}</ref> On 14 March, Shanghai confirmed one more imported case,<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://wsjkw.sh.gov.cn/xwfb/20200315/7b4878a4f5ee479da8a5e47d68683064.html|title=\u6628\u65e512-24\u65f6\uff0c\u4e0a\u6d77\u65b0\u589e1\u4f8b\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u5165\u578b\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u80ba\u708e\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b|date=2020-03-15|accessdate=2020-03-15|publisher=Shanghai Municipal Health Commission}}</ref> and Beijing also confirmed one more imported case from Italy.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://wjw.beijing.gov.cn/xwzx_20031/wnxw/202003/t20200315_1706294.html|title=\u5317\u4eac\u6628\u65e5\u65e0\u65b0\u589e\u62a5\u544a\u672c\u5730\u65b0\u51a0\u80ba\u708e\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b \uff0c\u65b0\u589e\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u51655\u4f8b\uff0c\u6cbb\u6108\u51fa\u96624\u4f8b|date=2020-03-15|accessdate=2020-03-15|publisher=Beijing Muni